because I'm afraid of you

286
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:27,320
but I'm afraid of your terrible songs.

287
00:17:28,600 --> 00:17:29,200
Wait.

288
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:30,000
What's up?

289
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:33,440
