292
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:39,200
Just wait for me.

293
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,040
Just do what I told you to.

294
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:40,920
Bye.

295
00:17:58,480 --> 00:17:59,280
Darling.

296
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:03,880
