Why will I have to nod and smile?

301
00:18:17,600 --> 00:18:19,600
Just do as I told you. Come on!

302
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:24,800
Are you Liu Siqi's boyfriend?

303
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:29,640
