379
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:36,360
Your sister is fine.

380
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,360
But I'm not fine.

381
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:41,320
Jincai and Tiancai

382
00:22:41,360 --> 00:22:42,520
go to work every day.

383
