386
00:22:50,360 --> 00:22:52,600
I didn't realize that it's so exhausting
to look after a child nowadays.

387
00:22:53,040 --> 00:22:54,360
I have to sterilize milk bottles

388
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,560
